        return 'xxxxxxxx-xxxx-4xxx-yxxx-xxxxxxxxxxxx'.replace(/[xy]/g, function(c) {
          var r, v;
          r = Math.random() * 16 | 0;
          v = c === 'x' ? r : r & 0x3 | 0x8;
          return v.toString(16);
        });
      };
      isUuid = /^[0-9a-f]{8}-[0-9a-f]{4}-[1-5][0-9a-f]{3}-[89ab][0-9a-f]{3}-[0-9a-f]{12}$/i;

        reqs = {};
        for (i = j = 1, ref = num; 1 <= ref ? j <= ref : j >= ref; i = 1 <= ref ? ++j : --j) {
          req = {
            id: getUuid(),
            num: i
          };
          if (i % 3 === 0) {
            req.x = i;
          } else if (i % 7 === 0) {
            req.y = i;
          } else {
            req.x = i;
            req.y = 2 * i;
          }
          reqs[req.id] = req;

        return reqs;

          req = reqs[id];

              if ('x' in req) {
                x.beginGroup(req.id);
                x.beginGroup('x');
                x.beginGroup(req.num);
                x.send(req.x);
                x.endGroup();
                x.endGroup();
                x.endGroup();
                x.disconnect();
              }
              if ('y' in req) {
                y.beginGroup(req.id);
                y.beginGroup('y');
                y.beginGroup(req.num);
                y.send(req.y);
                y.endGroup();
                y.endGroup();
                y.endGroup();
                return y.disconnect();
              }
            }, delay * req.num);
          })(req));
        }
        return results;
      };
